channel.title: Mopar Service
channel.description:
Hello moparscape! Recently I have noticed many people desperately seeking for help but getting none, so I decided to make a call service. Here's how it goes: I have set up my own VoiP System where you can call if you need help with your server or anything related to programming. The calls cost nothing since I pay 30€/month for the system so that you can call me any time any day.
Here is my number: (212) 247-7000. I live New York and 212 is the area code so dial all the numbers as they are written above^^. Btw, I'm not doing this alone, some of my friends are helping me so if there's many callers then you will have to wait a minute for the lines to open. Thank you.
